{
  "stem": "5471.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Later on, you learned that the pipes run from the gas ovens.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But whatever we tried during the war, we could never get to know what really happened.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we knew how it was in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know how it was in Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So to be on the safe side, keep them here and try to work against the Germans as much as possible.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] For instance, a funny incident-- at a certain time, everybody in Holland had to hand in all their copper articles.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Well, you don't do what the Germans ask, so we hid all our copper articles under, in the cellar.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My father had to do it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said, I'll teach them a lesson.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he took a bag where coal had in been, with a lot of coal dust.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he looked through his nails and he found some copper nails and he put them in the coal dust.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then he went to the office to hand them in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jep ?] said is that all you have got.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, isn't it enough, my father said and he turned to the [INAUDIBLE] and he was as black as-- little things you try to work against them, not to give them the way they wanted it.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not involved, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They never knew what we did either.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For instance, my father and mother came to us, then we were living outside a camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were not allowed to get into.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were just living on the outside of the camp and it was house eight.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were-- the Commander's house, the next one and another one.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
